@node Hist "How it all happened"

Beta versions:

▀191095:
   The programs are now fully localized. Catalogs included:
   English, Norsk, Nederlands, Italiano, Deutsch. More will come,
   hopefully. :)

▀161095:
   Fixed an EVIL bug that made 2.1 machines die.

▀151095:
   No longer packs #?.info files with the lha files.

▀131095:
   Fixed the installation script - now it actually sets the enviroment
   variables, and as Moods isn't a commodity yet, it doesn't put it in
   the WBStartup anymore, but in Sys:Prefs/ instead. The Setup program
   is now put in the Moods directory, whereever the user chose to place
   it.
   Added some code for localization.

▀111095:
   No more guru when the programs exited after being started from the
   WB (only a freak accident, but it's gone anyway). :)

▀091095:
   Now actually uses the GetVar() function for getting the enviroment
   variable.
   Added GuyBrush's installation script.
   Fixed the bug that occured when you tried to set to a mood while the
   program was started from the WB or another path.

▀061095:
   Added some "beta"-icons made by BeastyBoy.
   Changed the length limit of Mood names from 20 to 50 after several
   complaints by P-Gary.
   Setup: Now checks if each Mood actually HAS a datafile before it allows you
   to "Set To" that Mood.
   Moods: Now only lists the Moods that has datafiles. Exits after OK.

▀051095:
   Fixed some bugs that occured when P-Gary and Deadly4s pressed the wrong
   button at the wrong time. ;)

▀041095:
   First beta-release
@endnode

